We search 100% of the market on your behalf (agencies, private individuals, real estate agents, notaries, etc.).
You will have access to all the addresses of each property listed thanks to our exclusive relationship.
CONFIANCE IMMOBILIERE is committed!
We offer you a simple and effective method:
- Take the time to fully understand what you are looking for, advise you and study the project's viability;
- Refine your criteria by discussing an initial ‘broad’ selection with you;
- Search for properties matching your requirements on a daily basis, from 100% of the players on the market, no more and no less;
- Obtain detailed and precise information so that we only visit properties that are as relevant as possible to your property search;
- Organise all visits in the evening and during weekends, within a time slot that suits you;
- Help you draw up a purchase proposal;
- Negotiate the price of the property;
- Assemble all the necessary documents and assist you in signing the preliminary sales agreement and the sale contract.
